title: Scorpions-Live in London (043077)
description:
SCORPIONS-LIVE IN LONDON (LP Bootleg)

Ripped to mp3 256 kbit/s 

This is the best BOOTLEG I have ever heard by SCORPIONS
It was recorded off the sound board at Bolton University 04/30/77 
and is the SCORPIONS set test before they went to Japan to record Tokyo Tapes.
